*Rano* je sunčano i toplo. (It is sunny and warm early.)

Izašao je već *rano*. (He went out early.)

*Rani* jutarnji sjaj je prekrasan. (The early morning shine is beautiful.)

*Rano* se probudio i otišao na posao. (He woke up early and went to work.)

*Ranije* je bilo drugačije. (It was different before.)